                    <span>Hal Holbrook does a one man performance of a 70 year old Mark Twain, weaving together the stories and wit of the latter. I found Holbrook's portrayal to be annoying but any rendition of Twain is better than none at all.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">wry genius returned to life</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
